```
:::
:::


Use SymPy for finite sums.

::: {#1672161d .cell execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
import sympy as sp

i = sp.Symbol("i", integer=True, positive=True)
sp.summation(i, (i, 1, 5))
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display .cell-output-markdown execution_count=3}
$\displaystyle 15$
:::
:::
